From: Grimaldi Engineering <dev@grimaldi.engineering>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 15:17:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] feat(catalog): opt-in pricing model for standardized SKUs

Add optional price/priceUnit/purchasable fields to Product (non-breaking:
custom industrial goods stay quote-first). Price only the 3 standardized
SKUs (big bags, anti-aphid mesh, mulch) with clearly-marked PLACEHOLDER
prices to be replaced before launch. Add PEN/IGV formatting helpers and
show price on ProductCard when present.
